public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     delegate.process(exchange). }

// ******************** // Helpers // ******************** public static ServiceNowDispatcher on(final String action, final String subject, final Processor delegate) {     return new ServiceNowDispatcher(e -> matches(e.getIn(), action, subject), delegate). }

public static boolean matches(Message in, String action, final String subject) {     return ObjectHelper.equal(action, in.getHeader(ServiceNowConstants.ACTION, String.class), true) && ObjectHelper.equal(subject, in.getHeader(ServiceNowConstants.ACTION_SUBJECT, String.class), true). }
